    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-8 px-4">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-6">Reuse Tips</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Explore creative ways to reuse your items, from clothing to electronics!
        </p>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-4">Clothing</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li class="mb-2">Turn old t-shirts into cleaning rags.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Repurpose jeans into tote bags or storage organizers.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Use fabric scraps for patchwork projects.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Transform dresses into stylish skirts or blouses.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Donate clothes you no longer wear or have an exchange event with friends.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-4">Accessories</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li class="mb-2">Use old jewelry to create new pieces or upcycle them into decor.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Repurpose scarves as headbands or bag accessories.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Turn unused belts into wall art or unique plant hangers.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Transform brooches into hairpins or embellishments for bags.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-500 mb-4">Electronics</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                <li class="mb-2">Repurpose old smartphones as home security cameras or music players.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Turn broken tablets into digital photo frames.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Use old chargers as decorative cable organizers.</li>
                <li class="mb-2">Donate working electronics to schools or community centers.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
